# KIRA STUDIO

## Files
```
index.html   — UI markup (pages, modals, panels)
kira.css     — all styles
kira.js      — all logic (API calls, generation, batch, billing)
```

## Running

Must be served via HTTP (not opened as file://) for scripts to load.

**Python (easiest):**
```bash
cd /path/to/kira-studio
python3 -m http.server 8080
```
Then open: http://localhost:8080

**Node (if you have it):**
```bash
npx serve .
```

## API Keys
Set via ⚙ API KEY button in the top bar. Stored in browser localStorage.

| Key | Provider | Use |
|-----|----------|-----|
| kie.ai key | kie.ai | Default image generation |
| laozhang key | laozhang.ai | Cheapest images (USDT/Alipay) |
| WaveSpeed key | wavespeed.ai | Image fallback + ref hosting |
| EvoLink key | evolink.ai | Kling video (55% cheaper) |